Name: Kilroy Was Here
About the game: Stuck stranded alone in another dimension your only goal is to get back to your family, your life. Explore the C.U.B.E to find any information about where you actually are and how to get back, just remember to not go insane trying! Kilroy Was Here is an Interactive Fiction game where as the player you must traverse the 7 environments in search for their unqiue interaction points to try to gain a better understanding of the place you've ended up in and to try and find a way home. The More You Look The More You See. Features Unique Scenery: 7 Completely unique environments for you to explore. Simple Controls: Get straight into the game with basic and common controls. Steam Achievements: Show off to all your friends what you did in-game.
